    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "core_list",
      "x": 360,
      "y": 170,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 490,
      "text": "1. Identify issue\n2. Dependency check\n3. Context: ARCHITECTURE\n3b. Governance validation\n    · 8-dim table\n    · security-by-design\n    · ADD valid\n\n⛔ 3c. SPEC GATE\n    specs/ISSUE-XX.md there?\n    (hard gate — hook enforces)\n\n4. Plan + operator OK\n5. Implementation\n   · Code · docs · commit\n\n6. POST VALIDATION\n   6a. ESLint 0/0\n   6b. AC check + Linear\n   6c. Arch quick check\n   6d. Smoke test\n   6e. Security findings\n   6f. PASS / FAIL\n   6h. Remote CI loop · gh run watch\n\n7. Backlog update\n8. Result table",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1d1d1b",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
